Maps by Hop http://users.telepak.net/~rickyh/mapsbyho.htm</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usolarus2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>solarus2</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/01 6:15:03 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Changes to what we are proposing to Evade +more.</span><hr size=1> HEhehh, exactly right this evade plan is STUPID. Lets see you origianlyl intended evade to drop us at most to the 6th spot, but you increased teh hate list, so we are curently dropping to far, BUT now having us drop to 6th is no longer the idea??? <br>
<br>
