Second.  It was stated pretty clearly that the changes to evade were oversights from the begining and should have been changed long ago.  So NOW you come to us again and tell us that was was going to be done to Evade as a fix for what should have already been done is now not what you are actually going to do because it's not how it should be done either??  Come on!  I hate to say this for running the risk of never getting another Verant post again, but you all seem to be slightly clouded in your perspective and thoughts.<br>
